rComments: Generally awful lectures.  Unprepared, unorganized.  Sloppy.  Doesn't seem to care about students.  Exams seem to be fairly random and he offers no guidance or help at any point.  Misgraded my first exam twice, despite my clear explanation; eventually got the points.  Could have been a good class but wasn't.  Avoid.
unorganized lecture, exams diff a lot from regular assignments, avoid him if possible
Zoltan Furedi might be a good math advisor, but he does not care about the classes.  His lectures seemed unorganized and not very helpful.
